---
import Layout from '../layouts/layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="Alejandro Asensio">
  <main>
    <p class="text-subtext1">Hey, Alejandro here, from Barcelona.</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-none font-bold mb-16">
      I'm a front-end web developer who cares about <span
        class="bg-gradient-to-r from-flamingo via-pink to-mauve bg-clip-text text-transparent"
        >visual consistency</span
      > and
      <span
        class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal via-sky to-sapphire bg-clip-text text-transparent"
        >user experience</span
      >.
    </h1>
    <p class="text-subtext1">
      Currently, I'm building the front-end of the new platform for hospitality
      businesses at
      <a
        href="https://www.trustyou.com/"
        class="hover:text-peach hover:transition hover:duration-300">TrustYou</a
      >.
    </p>
    <p class="text-subtext1">
      To grab an idea of my previous work, check out my <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/aasensios/"
        class="hover:text-blue hover:transition hover:duration-300">LinkedIn</a
      > and my <a
        href="https://github.com/aasensios"
        class="hover:text-white hover:transition hover:duration-300">GitHub</a
      >.
    </p>
  </main>
</Layout>
